actions.message:
General Commands

>donate   this command is a command that allows u to donate to KBot
>help                                          dm's author commands
>play                                      plays the song mentioned
>clear queue                                     clears audio queue
>stop                                   disconnects and stops audio
>skip                                    skips current playing song
>translate                                  translates any language
>warnings                                check your/others warnings
>suggest                                suggests am edit to the bot
>serverinfo                 sends current server info of the server
>userinfo [user]                  sends mentioned users public info
>bank                                   check how much money u have
>curcon [ammount] [from currency] [to currency]      converts money
>jail [user]                      see for your self

actions.message:
Administrasive Commands
>warn [USER] [REASON]                         warns mentioned user
>clearwarn [USER]               clears warnings for mentioned user
>poll [DESC] [CHANNE            starts a poll in mentioned channel
>pm [MESSAGE]                       pm's all members in the server
>mute [USER]                                            Mutes User
>unmute [USER]                                        Un-Mute User
>rainbowrole [ROLE] [SPEED] Colour Changing Role For Role Mentioned
>announce [message]     sends announcement in announcements channel
